        &lt;ul type=&quot;circle&quot;>&#xD;
            &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;
                The rate of change of requirements over a period of observation&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;
